{"TopicId":200103,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Ksp tourism mod?","CreatedByName":"Yeepsta","CreatedById":209854,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-05T18:36:54Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Yeepsta","CreatedById":209854,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-05T18:36:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey everyone, I was wondering if anyone knows of a ksp mod that allows you to control your kerbal inside a spacecraft, so you can move them around the whole vessel and maybe even have added modules like a fitness center or a mess hall? Im thinking of building a tourist space station in low mun orbit, and it would be really nice to have a mod like this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-05T18:50:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/209854-yeepsta/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022209854\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/209854-yeepsta/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Yeepsta\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0There\u0027s this mod that allows free movement within spacecraft:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002226349\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1290716835\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/118371-wip-free-iva-alpha-v005-16x-2019-02-06/page/16/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:195px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnfortunately, it was last updated almost 2 years ago, so I wouldn\u0027t hold out much hope for it to work in a more recent KSP version.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-05T19:38:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI pretty sure that Connected Living Space has that feature, you can check the mod out here:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022113840\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed2767088505\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/192130-111-connected-living-spaces-adopted-2006-2020-12-29/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:195px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd for some really\u00A0nice space station parts that have really nice IVAs and add things like a fitness center,\u00A0check this mod out \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002283952\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed419783401\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/170211-111x-stockalike-station-parts-redux-december-27-2020/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:195px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-02-05T19:51:10Z\u0022 title=\u002202/05/2021 07:51  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 5, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by SpaceX_Boi\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Caerfinon","CreatedById":207619,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-05T20:06:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s this little gem also... Kerbals get just get up and move to other areas of the ship.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen